# Arrays and Basic Problem Solving

This repository contains my solutions to basic problem-solving
questions from HackerRank. The focus is on building core logic,
understanding fundamentals, and improving problem-solving skills.

Solutions are implemented using different programming languages
as required by the problem.

## Topics Covered
- Arrays
- Basic Problem Solving


## Problems Covered
- Count elements greater than previous average

## Platforms
- HackerRank

## Goal
To strengthen foundational programming concepts and develop
a strong base for advanced data structures and algorithms.

